Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.66,0:00:09.74,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.74,0:00:20.27,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:39.35,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:46.81,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:53.90,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:59.46,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.46,0:01:06.94,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.94,0:01:14.21,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.21,0:01:20.95,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.95,0:01:28.38,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:54.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.11,0:02:00.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone, the elder is summoning you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.12,0:02:04.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aira and Hanna are going\Nto give it a try today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.84,0:02:26.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ah, here she is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.85,0:02:34.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.08,0:02:37.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aira, Hanna...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:39.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you really sure you want to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.02,0:02:40.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:43.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,You know how long we've been\Npracticing towards this day!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:44.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad they chose me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:50.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's always been my dream to\Nbe like you and Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:52.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and to do the Emerald Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:57.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Dominüra and Sibylla Rimone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:03:03.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was they who bestowed us\Nwith the Emerald Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.15,0:03:06.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,And now our young girls\Nhave taken to the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:10.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,We have seen flowers blooming\Nthat had never bloomed before...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.36,0:03:13.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and we are now reaping the\Nharvest of our barren crops.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:18.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,And now today, we shall\Nsend off two more girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:22.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,I am certain that they, too,\Nshall bring us great fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:51.29,Titles,,90,0,0,,{\blur0.6}Their Portraits
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:04.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Get a move on! Let's not keep\Nthe client waiting forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.31,0:04:07.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.98,0:04:09.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, what is it, Wauf?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:11.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:13.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if\Nyou're a man or a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:16.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,...or even a former sibylla,\Nfor that matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:20.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,You work for me now! And I'm\Nnot cutting you any slack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:22.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, right, so what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:25.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you telling me to pick up the pace?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:28.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,You need to go easy on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:30.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:31.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, what is it, sweetheart?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:33.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mommy said...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:35.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,...to ask you what you wanted for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:39.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, everything your\Nmommy makes is so delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:41.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,She said you're not\Nallowed to say "anything"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:44.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,She did? All right, that's\Ngoing to be a tough one then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:52.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,So listen, this is the\Nmost critical time for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.47,0:04:55.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't want Waporif coming\Nafter me if you overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:05:00.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've heard that if you just keep moving,\Nyou can pop out the baby, 1-2-3!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.14,0:05:01.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:04.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,But thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:07.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,So what are we having for lunch, Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:09.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hm, let's see now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:13.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.52,0:05:14.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:18.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second, didn't you\Njust finish your night shift?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:19.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, we don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:22.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,The highlands and Shoukoku\Nare already waging a cold war.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:27.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,They could void the peace treaty any\Nday, and then they'll drag us into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:30.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,War again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:32.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Eliph! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:32.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.43,0:05:34.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:01.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,They saved us back there, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:02.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:04.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe was crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:06.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:09.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you think we'll succeed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.90,0:06:11.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:13.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.21,0:06:30.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,You've stolen a Simoun and\Nallowed the sibyllae to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:32.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you realize the magnitude\Nof what you've done?
Comment: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:36.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:39.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,If they should revolt\Nagainst our country...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:42.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,You've got the wrong idea.\NAll they're going to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:44.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,...is carry themselves away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:47.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,To the Land of Hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:04.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:05.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Play with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:09.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have a guest to tend to now, so\Nit'll have to be a little later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:12.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone, try to get along now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:15.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:18.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Such lively children!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:21.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know. It's all I can\Ndo to keep up with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:24.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta, I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:26.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,I tried to negotiate with them, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:28.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,...there's not much more I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:29.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roatreamon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:32.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,...this place wouldn't even\Nexist without your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:34.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I'm so grateful for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:37.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, there has to be\Nanother way. I'll find one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.96,0:07:40.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Once war is officially declared...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:44.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,...there will be more and more\Nvictims like these children.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:47.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're not really victims though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:51.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right. They've lost a\Nlot because of the war...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:54.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but they still have\Nso much to live for!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:57.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're our seeds of hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:08:01.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Their footsteps will one day\Nring out across the Land of Hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:03.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Of Hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.62,0:08:13.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,"The Land of Hope."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.19,0:08:16.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,For someone who was once\Na priestess long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:19.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,...those words have\Nsuch a nostalgic ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:22.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought it was only a legend.
Comment: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:25.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:29.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,But even if the legend is true...
Comment: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:31.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:36.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,...what purpose could there be in\Nperforming the Emerald Ri Majon now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:40.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's no longer any\Nvalue to the word "purpose."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:41.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anubituf...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.22,0:08:47.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, if we looked hard enough,\Nwe might find such a purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:49.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,But even if we'd found one...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.39,0:08:53.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the girls would never\Nhave chosen it themselves.
Comment: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:56.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:08:58.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:00.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simouns...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:06.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Take our Simouns and pursue\Nthe Sibylla Aurea's Simoun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:09.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you insane? Do you\Nintend to shoot them down?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:35.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:39.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our hands are tied. There's\Nnothing we can do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:42.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're going to go back to our jobs now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:43.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:52.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,It will be all right, Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:55.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,They'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:57.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even if they go after them now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.02,0:09:58.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,But, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:02.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that Aer and\NNeviril will make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:04.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's going to be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:07.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here, your nose is running!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:12.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Really, since when are\Nyou such a crybaby, Floe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:14.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,But, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:17.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe, there's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:18.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:22.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, come on. I'm\Nsure Aer and Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:23.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.96,0:10:25.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama, you're breathing on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:26.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,What? Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.57,0:10:29.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'm gonna get\Nall touchy-feely too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:31.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh? Then let's do that too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,— Para-sama!\N— Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:35.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come on! Stop it, Alty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:56.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Big Sister, was that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:58.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:04.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Big Sister! Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:07.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dad's clothes! Alty! Get that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:12.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, brother. All that time\Nwe spent doing laundry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:15.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,This weather's so weird. Guess we'll\Njust have to wash everything again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:17.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, all you do is sit\Nthere and watch, Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.98,0:11:20.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, that's my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:21.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:50.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:13.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling any better?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:18.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Thank you. My fever has gone down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:19.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.37,0:12:21.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.92,0:12:24.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think I finally understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:27.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,...what you meant after all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:30.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're all going to fly off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.61,0:12:33.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Into a sky where nothing\Nis ever certain...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:37.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Towards a hope that they\Ncan't even be sure exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.25,0:12:41.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,I made everyone learn how\Nto do the Emerald Ri Majon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:43.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,...yet I don't even\Ntake to the skies myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:45.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:48.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rimone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:50.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you want to fly again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.23,0:12:52.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:55.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,But if you don't want\Nto do it, Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:58.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll never fly with anyone as my pair...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:13:01.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but you, Dominüra.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.65,0:13:15.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:21.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.70,0:13:25.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Simouns!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:26.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're coming after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:29.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,— Neviril!\N— Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:30.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry! They're\Ngoing to catch up to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.98,0:13:32.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,— Wait.\N— What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:37.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're going to do a Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:38.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'd better hurry up then!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:41.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,No. That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:44.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:46.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've never seen that Ri Majon before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:48.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Morning Calm Ri Majon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:51.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morning Calm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:54.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,I read about that one\Nonce in an old book.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:57.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's performed to bid farewell to\Ncomrades about to depart on a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.85,0:14:01.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,To bid farewell to comrades\Ndeparting on a journey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:12.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:14.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Morning Calm Ri Majon?
Comment: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:21.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:25.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,There was also a time in my life...
Comment: 0,0:14:26.29,0:14:28.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Foreign
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.86,0:14:31.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,Long ago, we were all maidens too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:55.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:56.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:14:58.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:09.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go now, Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.87,0:15:12.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,To a place where you and I can be free!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.94,0:15:15.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes. Let's go, Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.89,0:15:27.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Forgive me for bringing\Nyou here, Rimone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:28.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's all right. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.79,0:15:33.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,You see, I want you to pair up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:37.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,I already told you no once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:38.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll only...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:40.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:46.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,But does Dominüra ever intend\Nto fly again? I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:52.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.28,0:15:54.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.36,0:16:13.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um, wasn't that a Simoun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:15.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:17.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.78,0:16:19.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that a name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:22.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,The ultimate form of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:25.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Love?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:26.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:29.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:32.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,The ultimate love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:35.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Which sky shall we journey towards next?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:37.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:11.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey! You got here early, Vura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.86,0:17:13.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, wait. I mean Vuraf.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:15.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's awkward for you\Nto call me that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:16.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can just call me Vura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:19.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, Vura. Why\Ndon't you come inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:20.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:27.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did you get one too, Vura?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:28.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:31.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,The war hasn't even started yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.52,0:17:33.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess former sibyllae...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:36.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,...have the honor of being the first\Nto be shipped out at times like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:38.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Which side?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:41.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,My hometown is on the\Nother side of the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:43.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll be fighting for Shoukoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:45.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,So we're going to be enemies then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:46.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.66,0:17:52.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Never mind. Here, have some of our\Nlocal vegetables! New strain, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.70,0:17:54.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,I need to make a killing on these...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:58.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and find myself a lovely bride.\NI can't die till I've done that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.77,0:18:02.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Becoming a man hasn't\Nchanged you at all, Floef!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:06.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's hard to say, isn't it?\NYou can just call me Floe too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:16.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that the Arcus Prima?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:21.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I thought I might as well\Nlive where I can always see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:23.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why I picked this spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:25.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,A sunken luxury liner?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:27.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,I suppose there's an allure to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:29.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,See you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:31.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:33.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait, that might be bad luck to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:36.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see\Nyou on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.18,0:18:39.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right then. How's goodbye?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:41.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:42.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:09.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder why none of us could let it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:14.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,The idea of sending Aer and\NNeviril off to that other world?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:20.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Was it because we wanted to defy\Nthe inescapable flow of time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:23.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,We were afraid to grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:25.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,We wanted to stay the way\Nwe were as young girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:28.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did we project those feelings\Non to Aer and Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:31.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, I'm sure that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:35.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,All we wanted to do\Nwas to leave our mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:39.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,To prove that we once\Nexisted, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:42.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,We wanted to shout that\Nout to the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:47.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,The fact that we were\Nonce really here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:50.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,We wanted to leave our mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:53.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,We wanted to raise our voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:03.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:04.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:09.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder where you are right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:17.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where are you, our eternal maidens?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.89,0:20:33.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Such a nice breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:35.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:36.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,It certainly is a nice breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:47.90,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.90,0:22:52.14,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.14,0:22:59.21,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.21,0:23:06.81,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.62,0:23:19.70,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,"I want to get closer to you."\N"I want to feel your pulse."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.70,0:23:24.87,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.87,0:23:28.85,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.85,0:23:32.88,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.88,0:23:38.75,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.75,0:23:44.30,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the sky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.30,0:23:47.73,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.73,0:23:53.40,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.40,0:23:59.63,Lyrics bottom,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
